{"tid":1040240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<大灣區資訊>月入16000扣稅後只剩11500","createTime":"2019-02-28T03:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T11:49:29.000Z","uid":144372,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c5df4785b755c92e8c23de56faac6a79c788b2","tid":1040240,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/156743691.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhidao.baidu.com%2Fquestion%2F156743691.html&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Tdz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ecc6a4c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/156743691.html</a><br />\n稅前薪水16000，都按國家五險一金交，完稅後拿到手多少？<br />\n<br />\n紙墨成殤<br />\n來自百度知道認證團隊2018-11-11<br />\n展開全部<br />\n薪水16000元，扣除&ldquo;五險一金&rdquo;和&ldquo;個人所得稅&rdquo;後，實際到手薪水11588元。<br />\n1、養老保險：組織繳納比例各地各企業不一致，自己繳納8%，16000*8%=1280元。<br />\n2、醫療保險：組織繳納比例各地各企業不一致，自己繳納2%，16000*2%=320元。<br />\n3、失業保險：自己繳納1%，16000*1%=160元。<br />\n4、工傷保險：組織每個月為你繳納0.5%，自己一分錢不繳。<br />\n5、生育保險：組織每個月為你繳納0.8%，自己一分錢不繳。<br />\n6、住房公積金：組織每個月繳納8%，自己繳納12%，16000*12%=1920元。<br />\n7、個人所得稅：按照最新稅率計算，除扣除5000元的基數外，還要扣除&ldquo;五險一金&rdquo;以及其他專項附加等費用，（16000-5000-1280-320-160-1920）*10%=732元。"},{"pid":"e22eca8289dd127bba7a2a7efece586eb23eb4ba","tid":1040240,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7af9e51f3423c4eaecf02ef2a3eb3416b765457","tid":1040240,"uid":26306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"搵鬼住"},{"pid":"93d2e19b475d90fb120d82f0446c25e60f73e758","tid":1040240,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"依個要bookmark先"},{"pid":"90b9d68453f3676019af53b9e496a69c9aa23ab0","tid":1040240,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as